{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "ews-api-collection-v2",
    "name": "EWS API - Early Warning System",
    "description": "API Documentation for EWS (Early Warning System) - FIK Campus\n\n## Roles:\n- **Dekan**: Akses seluruh data fakultas (semua prodi)\n- **Kaprodi**: Akses data hanya untuk prodi sendiri\n- **Mahasiswa**: Akses data profil pribadi\n\n## Base URL: {{api_base}}",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "00 - Authentication",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Login Dekan",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('HTTP 200', function () { pm.response.to.have.status(200); });",
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json && json.success && json.data && json.data.access_token) {",
                  "  pm.environment.set('access_token', json.data.access_token);",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{email_dekan}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{password}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{api_base}}/login-dekan",
              "host": ["{{api_base}}"],
              "path": ["login-dekan"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
